2003-12-10 15:06  golda

	* cgi-bin/webglimpse.cgi: Fixed dumb error - use last not break

2003-12-06 13:50  golda

	* cgi-bin/webglimpse.cgi: Fix typo varnames

2003-12-06 12:09  golda

	* cgi-bin/webglimpse.cgi, templates/wgany.html: Add 'alternate'
	option to Webglimpse to search in first available archive, to allow
	for two equivalent archives to be indexed at different times.  This
	will allow you to keep a large index available 100% of the time -
	when one is indexing, the other will be used.  Thanks to Peter
	Moore for the clever idea!

