2003-11-12 13:07  golda

	* cgi-bin/webglimpse.cgi: cleaner defaults when parsing search
	results - we were assuming the right pattern of glimpse output, but
	in cases like when they changed the FILE_END_MARK, the pattern
	could be wrong.  This used to result in glimpse command lines in
	the search results output.  Now the output will be blank if the
	FILE_END_MARK doesn't match.

