	* lib/: wgHeader.pm, wgSite.pm, wgSiteConf.pm: Main change is to
	wgSiteConf.pm - don't load all passwd entries for goodness sake! 
	This can take a looong time on some systems.  Was done since
	ancient times to process UserDir settings but way too much overhead
	to do every time on startup.
	
