	* lib/CustomOutputTool.pm: Two major changes -
	
		1) now allow [INCLUDE: filename] in begin_html and end_html
	vars, so user can get their own look & feel without doing a lot of
	hand-editing of twgoutput.cfg
	
		2) Now allow .wgoutputfields to include var of type TEXT or
	VARTEXT, so a user can define a fixed text custom output field or
	one containing other available variables.

