2002-05-31 07:39  golda

	* templates/wgreindex: Do not use -f (incremental index) by
	default; can make inefficient index after a while, especiall if
	files are removed as well as added.  Also in at least 1 case has
	been associated with index errors (not reproducible yet). 
	Generally we ssume search speed is more important than indexing
	speed, so default to clean full reindex.

