2001-11-29 21:28  golda

	* templates/wgall.html: Just changing text to "WebglimpseII"

2001-11-29 21:28  golda

	* lib/wgSiteConf.pm: LocalFile2URL now looks for the longest match
	to the directory path in all known local domains.  Before it was
	just returning the first one found,which might not be what you want
	if you have a subdirectory aliased to another domain.  We sort the
	list of possible paths ahead of time so it doesn't take longer than
	before.

