	* dist/wgfilter-index: Avoid loops when using Zeus webserver,
	thanks to Gerry Magennis for the fix!

2001-11-04 17:15  golda

	* lib/: d, wgTextMsgs.pm: Search from command-line interface

2001-11-03 18:46  golda

	* lib/: wgSiteConf.pm, wgTextMsgs.pm: Minor typo fixes

2001-11-03 14:09  golda

	* lib/AllowDeny.pm: Allow spaces before comments.

2001-11-03 14:09  golda

	* TODO: [no log message]

2001-10-31 14:17  golda

	* lib/: d, stall.pl, wgSite.pm, wgSiteConf.pm, wgTextMsgs.pm:
	command-line interface working

2001-10-22 23:44  golda

	* TODO, wgcmd, wginstall.pl, cgi-bin/wgarcmin.cgi,
	lib/CommandWeb.pm, lib/wgArch.pm, lib/wgConf.pm, lib/wgHeader.pm,
	lib/wgSiteConf.pm, lib/wgTextMsgs.pm, templates/tmplManageAll.html:
	Added command-line interface, wgcmd, for managing archives.
	
	You can use wgcmd instead of the web interface, wgarcmin.cgi.  It
	doesn't do quite as many things for you, because you can also edit
	the configuration files directly.  wgcmd is mainly useful for
	creating new archives, adding docs to an existing archive, and
	listing all the archives on your server.  If you have multiple
	indexes it is very useful to list them all in one place!
	
	Other changes are support for new wgcmd.  Also wginstall.pl now has
	an option to create archive at end of install, like in 1.7.

2001-10-22 17:24  golda

	* templates/hebrew/wgoutput.cfg: Minor text corrections - thanks to
	Adeena!

