2001-07-07 23:00  golda

	* wginstall.pl: Default to htuml2txt lex script from Christian
	Vogler; it is fastest filter that has been thoroughly tested.

2001-07-06 23:27  golda

	* templates/.glimpse_filters: Adding '.jhtml' to the list of
	html-type extensions to filter

2001-07-06 23:25  golda

	* templates/hebrew/wgindex.html: Defaulting to Use Filters=yes

2001-07-06 23:25  golda

	* cgi-bin/webglimpse.cgi, lib/RankHits.pm: Correcting regexp
	matching glimpse lines, when there is no title Glimpse doesn't
	output the file-end-mark after the URL.  We can safely treat the
	url as [^\s]+ because URL's never have spaces (they're converted to
	%20's).  This was really slowing down some searches, as much as
	30seconds.  It only affected files not ending in html/htm.

2001-07-06 23:21  golda

	* wginstall.pl: Version #

2001-07-03 23:55  golda

