	confarc.

2001-03-27 18:34  golda

	* lib/: , nh, wgArch.pm: Don't use rm -rf in a script!	Change to
	explicitly delete just the files we put there, then rmdir.  Also
	don't complain about unconfigured domains for SITE, TREE type
	roots.

2001-03-26 23:37  golda

	* makenh: Use $FILE_END_MARK in .wgmapfile to match .wg_toindex. 
	Actually, I think we can remote .wgmapfile altogether - looks like
	it is an old artifact now replaced by .wg_toindex.  Except, that
	now we are using it to read list of saved files, could use
	.wg_toindex instead.

2001-03-26 22:35  golda

	* lib/: file, nh, httpget.c: Touch retrieved files with
	Last-Modified: time from http header line.  We need this so we can
	compare exact times when doing an If-Modified-Since, because many
	httpd servers only return Unmodified if the timestamp matches
	exactly.  (This is in case someone replaces a file with an older
	version, so that it will seem to be modified if the timestamp does
	not match exactly).

2001-03-26 17:44  golda

	* templates/tmplAddTree.html: Use value of 1 for follow-to-remote
	flags rather than text strings.

2001-03-26 15:16  golda

	* lib/: nh, stall.pl, httpget.c, wgHeader.pm, wgRoot.pm: Don't
	retrieve remote files if we have a current copy saved.	Now we move
	.remote to .remote.old temporarily during indexing, and if a file
	we want to retrieve is there we use the date HTTP parameter to
	retrieve a new version only if more current.

2001-03-07 16:47  golda

	* templates/wgreindex: Put -o switch back into glimpseindex command
	line!  Had been accidentally left out of wgreindex template.

2001-02-08 20:15  golda

	* lib/wgSiteConf.pm: use "my" instead of "local" - old code hanging
	around

2001-02-08 20:15  golda

	* wginstall.pl: modified to use require instead of use
	Term::ReadKey

2001-02-08 19:51  golda

	* wginstall.pl: Changed use Term::ReadKey to require, because
	returns value for eval.  Not sure why eval("use Term::ReadKey") was
	returning false even when the use succeeded - maybe compile-time vs
	runtime issue?

2001-01-31 21:25  golda

	* lib/wgHeader.pm: Fix HTMLFILE_RE to have \. instead of . in the
	pattern - can't believe this went uncaught for so many years! 
	Thanks to Brett Bendickson for pointing it out!

2001-01-31 21:25  golda

	* makenh: Check explicitly if StartDir is a file or directory,
	don't depend on matching a pattern!  Thanks to Brett Bendickson for
	pointing this out.

2001-01-31 00:07  golda

	* cgi-bin/wgarcmin, lib/wgArch.pm, lib/wgErrors.pm, lib/wgRoot.pm,
	templates/tmplManageArch.html: Index in background instead of
	foreground; the browser dropping the session in the middle of long
	index processes was causing problems.
	
	Added an "update status" link so the user can check when indexing
	is complete.
	
	Should also provide a report on the last index...

