2001-01-29 22:57  golda

	* lib/wgRoot.pm: If user adds a DIR type root without specifying
	the equiv URL, try to guess it; if unsuccessful, do not add the
	root. (Was adding a root with blank URL, this caused problems
	because the URL is the unique identifier of a root.)
	
	Minor style change to templates.

