	* templates/: , , pl, arcmin, .pm, .pm, tmplAddDir.html,
	tmplAddSite.html, tmplAddTree.html, tmplEditDir.html,
	tmplEditSite.html, tmplEditTree.html: makenh, wgRoot.pm: use
	wgRoot->Get{Hops} instead of raw value; a large value will be
	substituted for a Site type archive with 0 hops (interpreted as no
	limit based on hops).
	
