2001-01-23 12:34  golda

	* addsearch, confarc, rmarc, lib/wgHeader.pm, templates/wgreindex:
	Modifying addsearch to use new wgConf, wgArch modules instead of
	manually looking for archive info.  Will need to be run by hand,
	not as the web user, on most installations.
	
	wgreindex no longer tries to call addsearch itself for now
	
	confarc has been replaced by wgarcmin
	
	rmarc is no longer needed, archives can be removed by a call to
	wgArch->Destroy

2001-01-22 13:37  golda

	* TODO, addsearch, cgi-bin/webglimpse, lib/ResultCache.pm,
	lib/wgArch.pm, lib/wgRoot.pm, templates/wgall.html: Added
	MakeDirOptions procedure to generate the options in wgall.html
	(limit search by subdirectory)
	
