	* cgi-bin/webglimpse, lib/ResultCache.pm: Try to find cache file
	even on first time doing a search; the exact same search may have
	already been done.

2001-01-15 01:11  golda

	* lib/: , bin/webglimpse, CustomOutputTool.pm, OutputTool.pm,
	ResultCache.pm: Rewrote ResultCache.pm (& calling Webglimpse
	routines) to:	     - expire old cache files every time it is run 
	 - read arbitrary N lines from cache without modifying the cache
	file	- name cache files by glimpse cmd so they can be used by
	other users    - CustomOutputTool now outputs toolbar for jumping
	to arbitrary N hits  (instead of always "Next N hits")	     - use
	ptr file to speed cache accesses Still a few bugs - doesn't work
	correctly in conjunction with RankHits.pm.
	
	Mostly works, pretty fast.

2000-12-26 23:59  golda

	* templates/tmplNewArch.html: Added Open Directory Project credits
	& link box

2000-12-26 22:40  golda

	* templates/tmplManageAll.html: [no log message]

2000-12-26 20:01  golda

	* lib/: stall.pl, /wgODP3.db, /wgODP3.dbm.dir, /wgODP3.dbm.pag,
	CatTree.pm, wgHeader.pm: Switched to SDBM after all, because it
	turns out that compressed, the SDBM data files are actually smaller
	than DB_File format so the download time will be a bit faster, and
	SDBM is bundled with Perl so it will be supported on all systems.

2000-12-26 19:49  golda

	* dist/wgODP3.db, lib/CatTree.pm: Added category module &
	distribute w/1st 3 levels of dmoz cats in DB_File format.  (Only
	takes 274Kb; SDBM format is about 450Kb, the original RDF files are
	huge - 100's of Mb)

2000-12-26 19:45  golda

	* templates/: , pl, arcmin, .pm, er.pm, tmplManageArch.html,
	tmplNewArch.html: Added category support.

