2000-12-05 23:53  golda

	* dist/glimpse-eye.jpg: Moved glimpse-eye.jpg into /lib
	subdirectory for easier access by cgi scripts.	(WEBGLIMPSE_LIB is
	the only variable replaced in all files, so we can access it with
	more certainty.)

2000-12-05 23:52  golda

	* lib/wgArch.pm, templates/tmplManageArch.html: Removed -q switch
	when wgreindex is run from web so results will show up in window. 
	May want to make this optional for really large archives.  Removed
	extra "Search" button.

2000-12-05 23:40  golda

	* templates/: , pl, owimg.sh, arcmin, .pm, tmplAddDir.html,
	wgindex.html: Added showimg.sh script to be able to display the
	glimpse eye logo from a cgi script without having to make the user
	set up an "images" directory under document root just for this one
	file.
	
	Also modified wgarcmin to regenerate template files each time "Save
	Changes" is pressed.  This way the new archive name, etc can get
	put into the search page.  If a user wants to hand-edit these
	files, they should make copies not in the archive directory, or
	edit the master copies in the webglimpse home dir.

2000-12-05 22:03  golda

	* templates/: , dWeb.pm, .pm, Conf.pm, tmplEditTree.html,
